                  <handDesc>
                    <handNote xml:id="h1" script="Ethiopic">
                    <seg type="rubrication">
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኢግዚአብሔር፡</foreign>
                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡</foreign>
                    </seg>
                    <desc>The word God is rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works</desc>
                    <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#103v" facs="106">fols. 103v, </locus> (Ps. 148); <locus target="#104v" facs="107">104v, </locus> (Ps. 150); completely unique approach to tenth biblical canticle (<locus target="#112r #112v #113r #113v" facs="114 115 116">112r, 112v, 113r, 113v</locus>) with “all works of God praise Him” in black ink and the response “he is glorfied and exalted forever” in red ink</desc>
                    </handNote>
                    </handDesc>
                  <decoDesc>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#ir(ecto)" facs="001">Fol. ir(ecto)</locus><desc>crude drawing of a face, in ink</desc></decoNote>
                  	<decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#iv(erso)" facs="002">Fol. iv(erso)</locus><desc>crude drawing of person, in pencil</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="003">Fol. iiv(erso)</locus><desc>crude drawing of two horses or cattle, in blue ink</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d4"><locus target="#137r" facs="139">Fol. 137r</locus><desc>crude drawing of person and horse, in blue ink</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d5">
                      Decorative designs:
                      <locus target="#1r #36v #70r #105r #122v" facs="003 039 072 107 125">folss. 1r, 36v, 70r, 105r, 122v, </locus> (ḥaräg);
                      <locus target="#1r #7r #13v #30r #36r #41r #49r #58r #65r #81r #91v #94r #99r #116v" facs="003 009 016 032 038 043 051 060 067 083 094 096 101 119">1r, 7r, 13v, 30r, 36r, 41r, 49r, 58r, 65r, 81r, 91v, 94r, 99r, 116v, </locus> (line of alternating red and black dots);
                      <locus target="#128v #135v" facs="131 138">128v, 135v</locus> (multiple full stops)
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
